room_title: Escape room "A.I. Rebellion" by Brain Drain in Chicago
room_description:
Artificial Intelligence was created to serve us, but what if something goes wrong and it gets out of our control? Michael Hall, a talented and famous scientist who created first the A.I. machine, has disappeared following the death of his wife.
You belong to a group of scientists who worked closely with Michael and who can solve the mystery. You will need to gain access to his lab and if you manage to get to the end you will need to make a decision whether to destroy Michaelâ€™s creation or to change this world forever.
